Package com.ttc.fitPT.ptSchedule.model

Class Schedule

java.lang.Object
com.ttc.fitPT.ptSchedule.model.Schedule
public class Schedule extends Object
Represents a schedule entry for a therapist, including the date, start time, and end time of availability.
